title: Person Of Interest.John Season 1 Episode 1 Subway Scene
author: Sabrina Estampe
comment:
Other great Reese quotes:  
"I'll show him what a real monster looks like."
"Maybe it's up to me to do what good people can't."
"I don't particularly like killing people, but I'm very good at it."
Reese had sooooo much character development in this show. Especially in season 4. Poor guy

Even while drunk as hell, Reese's gun senses are off the roof!
Why does that guy in red think he need a gun to beat a hobo anyways?
Am going to miss this series a lot.....
0:52 The big sigh Reese does. "l didn't want to fight today but it looks like I may have too."
